1. Čuo sam mnogo *teorija* o poreklu reči "vampir". (I've heard many *theories* about the origin of the word "vampire".)
2. Koje *teorije* podržavate o nastanku života na Zemlji? (What *theories* do you support about the origin of life on Earth?)
3. Profesor je predstavio različite *teorije* o ekonomskim krizama. (The professor presented various *theories* about economic crises.)
4. Ona voli da čita knjige o *teoriji* relativiteta. (She likes to read books about the *theory* of relativity.)
5. Da li si ikada čuo *teoriju* da su dinosauri izumrli zbog udara asteroida? (Have you ever heard the *theory* that dinosaurs became extinct due to an asteroid impact?)
6. Poslodavci često primenjuju *teoriju* motivacije putem bonusa. (Employers often apply the *theory* of motivation through bonuses.)
7. Njegova *teorija* o tome zašto ljudi spavaju je veoma interesantna. (His *theory* about why people sleep is very interesting.)
8. Našli su novi dokaz koji podržava *teoriju* o postojanju crnih rupa. (They found new evidence supporting the *theory* of the existence of black holes.)
9. Postoji *teorija* da su psi nasledili svoju sposobnost za miris od vukova. (There's a *theory* that dogs inherited their sense of smell from wolves.)
10. Njegova *teorija* o tome kako pobediti na izborima nije se pokazala tačnom. (His *theory* on how to win elections didn't prove to be accurate.)